text: Mehmet Esenceli (born 1940) is a Turkish wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 52 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Turkish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Turkey Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Kahramanmaraş
